Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是好幾年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我與數碼獸邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DIGIMON ADVENTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.80,0:01:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光 你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太一 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽要出去了，好好照顧小光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了，真是個奇怪的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽…  媽媽 媽媽 小光她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那蛋放下吧 不礙事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想把它怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說是從電腦裏面鑽出來的話，誰都不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢 這個蛋也真大 可以做個大煎蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的啦 對不起 快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 乖乖地不要動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼動物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是貓?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從蛋出來的應該是鳥吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這傢伙還真能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家裏的東西都給你吃光了 小波波
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是小波波
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小胖豬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小黑球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道叫黑惡魔啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等媽媽回來了要怎樣跟她說呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，這裏是八神家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!小光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 那傢伙怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 便便了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:06:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼看 都不像是一般的動物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它會吃這種東西嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個傢伙…  小光不能吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!住 住 住 住 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西 還是趕緊丟出去的好!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咪咪 停手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說叫你別追了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你連貓都打不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我買了蛋糕回來 要不要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩 我馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是吃咖喱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸(Koromon)說它也想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼滾球獸?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你給它起的名字嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咪咪的事很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 但是真的很嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光 它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫光 小光(Hikari)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥叫太一 太一(Taichi)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太一和小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它…  會說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是朋友的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友的…  證明?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又便便了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 這…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾 滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說話啊 滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光 太一 小光 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樣 樣子又…  變…  了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進門的時候輕一點好不好 你當現在是什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看你 一身的酒臭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太一 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別叫啊 會吵醒他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺前要親親他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎?打不開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 太一 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了他們已經睡了 別吵醒了好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你老是不替別人考慮考慮 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光 別做傻事 快下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太一 怎麼了? 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太一 這麼晚你去哪裏 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底跑哪裏去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸 你不跟我說話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸 住手 滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊 滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我們回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 有隻鳥 非常大的鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳥…  鳥?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像被打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 被壓在下面了 喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是… ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸 滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸 滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光 別過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸它 滾球獸它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸 快站起來 滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸 你去哪裏了 滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一次匆匆的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(滾球獸 你去哪裏了 滾球獸 滾球獸)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一隻不能在我們的世界裏相見的怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:19:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾球獸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在 我在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,----------蝴蝶片尾-----------
